# PromptLab — Blueprint-Based Analyzer Walkthrough

## Architecture Rewrite

The analyzer was completely rewritten from a word-scanning engine to a **blueprint-based structural comparison** engine.

### 6-Step Architecture

```
User Prompt → Intent Extraction → Blueprint Lookup (model×task)
           → Structural Comparison → Mechanical Scoring → Scoped Suggestions
```

